data.text:
McMinnville resident and Woodbury, TN native Mary Frances Neal, age 76, was born March 13, 1948 and died May 19, 2024 at NHC Healthcare in McMinnville following an extended illness.

A former employee of Aquatech, she was the daughter of the late Lanis and Mildred Myers. In addition to her parents, she was preceded in death by brothers, Jackie Myers and David Myers.

Ms. Neal is survived by daughters, Shelia Brenneman and Sherry Bittner, both of McMinnville; grandchildren, Sandy (Tim) Harris and Joshua Neal; great-grandchildren, Elexia Byars, Damian Neal and Dominic Neal; brother, Tony (Brenda) Myers of McMinnville; sisters, Daisy, Peggy Byars, Patsy (Mickey) Davis, Lucy (Gary) Webster and Louise (Rickey) McCormick and several nieces and nephews.

Per Ms. Neal’s wishes, she will be cremated. No service or visitation will be held at High’s.

Online condolences may be made at www.highfuneralhome.com.

High Funeral Home and High’s Cremations, Inc. are in charge of arrangements.
